source.name: Could not process some files due to syntax errors

markdownMessage: A parse error occurred: Expecting Unicode escape sequence \\uXXXX. Check the syntax of the file. If the file is invalid, correct the error or [exclude](https://docs.github.com/en/code-security/code-scanning/automatically-scanning-your-code-for-vulnerabilities-and-errors/customizing-code-scanning) the file from analysis.
